    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is a blank canvas ready for someone with a mechanical touch to bring it back to life. While it currently needs significant TLC and some major repairs to get back to its best, it offers a great opportunity to own a classic model at a fraction of the cost. If you're looking for a rewarding project or a reliable source for parts, this is the one for you!",
