    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in reliable running order. It requires significant mechanical work, including engine diagnostics and potential transmission repairs, before it can be safely driven on the road. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches and several dents, while the interior needs a deep cleaning and some upholstery repair. This is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts vehicle, and it is sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 4000.0,
