    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, primarily as a parts car or a major restoration project for a dedicated hobbyist. The exterior suffers from significant rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, and the paint is heavily oxidized across all surfaces. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission is currently slipping; additionally, the interior shows heavy wear with several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. While it is not currently roadworthy, it could serve as a valuable source of components or a base for someone with the tools and time for a full rebuild.",
      "price": 4500.0,
